'''泰化'''（{{lang-en|Thaification}}）是指[[泰国|泰国]]嘗試同化不同民族与文化入中央泰人文化中。这个政策是20世纪泰国成为一个[[民族国家|民族国家]]后出现。

==行动==
泰化是1930年代，[[銮披汶·颂堪|銮披汶·颂堪]]政变掌權后的泰民族主义政策，他们推行同化政策想將[[泰国华人|泰国华人]]等少数民族同化成泰人，[[泰语|泰语]]成为官方语言，泰族文化成为官方文化。每天播两次国歌，一次在早上8:00，另一次在傍晚18:00。

==目标==
泰化最主要目标是欲同化泰王国周边的民族：東北的[[老族|老族]]、[[泰北|泰北]]山区部落、南部[[马来人|马来人]]、[[孟族|孟族]]与泰国華人<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ganjanakhundee|first1=Supalak|title=Lao are lazy: The problem with 'Thai superiority'|url=http://www.nationmultimedia.com/politics/Lao-are-lazy-The-problem-with-Thai-superiority-30296890.html|accessdate=6 October 2016|work=The Nation|date=5 October 2016|format=Opinion|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411040737/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/politics/Lao-are-lazy-The-problem-with-Thai-superiority-30296890.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|ref=harv|last=Ivanoff|first=Jacques|title=The Cultural Roots of Violence in Malay Southern Thailand: Comparative Mythology; Soul of Rice|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=F_RKmwEACAAJ|year=2010|publisher=White Lotus Company Limited}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Haji Umar|first1=Umaiyah|title=The Assimilation of Bangkok-Melayu Communities in the Bangkok Metropolis and Surrounding Areas|date=2003|isbn=9789749121344}}</ref>。泰化方法是要他们说中央泰语与禁止泰国華人進入華人学校<ref name=Identities>{{Cite book|title=Alternate Identities: The Chinese of Contemporary Thailand|url=https://archive.org/details/alternateidentit00chee|author=Tong, Chee Kiong|author2=Chan, Kwok Bun |publisher=[[Brill_Publishers|Brill Publishers]]|year=2001|pages=[https://archive.org/details/alternateidentit00chee/page/170 170]–177}}</ref>。

